<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.3.10">
<l>āyiran tōḷparappi muṭiyāyiram miṉṉilaka</l>
<l>āyiram paintalaiya vaṉantacayaṉa ṉāḷumalai</l>
<l>āyira māṟukaḷuñ cuṉaikaḷpala vāyiramum</l>
<l>āyiram pūmpoḻilu muṭaimāliruñ cōlaiyatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain where reigns he whose bed is Aṉanta</l>
<l rend="indent">with a thousand green heads,</l>
<l rend="indent">as [his] thousand arms spread [wide],</l>
<l rend="indent">[and his] thousand crowns glitter [like] lightning,</l>
<l>that is Māliruñcōlai with a thousand flower groves,</l>
<l rend="indent">a thousand rivers, and many thousand mountain springs!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
